    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/charles_jules_henry_nicol_299880",
        "quote": "I demonstrated the characteristics of experimental fever. It appears after an incubation period which is never less than five days. It follows the same pattern as natural fever in man, but is of shorter duration and less pronounced.",
